  <name>Currency Converter</name>
  <summary>A simple currency converter using Google-based data</summary>
  <description>
    <p>The currency converter is simple and fast, ideal for those who need to convert currencies repeatedly.</p>
  </description>
  <url type="homepage">https://github.com/ideveCore/currency-converter</url>
